  <body>
    <p>You can add a new row using the <uicontrol>Copy</uicontrol>/<uicontrol>Paste</uicontrol>
      actions, or by selecting <uicontrol><image href="../img/TableRow16.gif" id="image_xsq_2xz_tr"
        /> Insert row</uicontrol> from the contextual menu or the toolbar.</p>
    <p>For a faster way to insert a new row, move the selection over the row header, and then press
        <uicontrol conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/enter"/>. The row header
      is the zone in the left of the row that holds the row number. The new row is inserted below
      the selection.</p>
  </body>
